explanation: This solution uses a HashMap to count the occurrences of each number in the array, and then a HashSet to store the unique counts. The time complexity is O(n) because we iterate through the array once, and the space complexity is also O(n) because in the worst case, all numbers in the array are unique and we store all of them in the HashMap and HashSet.

